data.description: SELLERS ARE MOTIVATED, PLEASE BRING US AN OFFER. Country living at its finest! This four-bedroom home is situated on approximately two acres on a rural road, in the Bemus Point School District. This one is move-in ready, nothing major needs done here. The main floor has the spacious master bedroom with a roomy closet, a second bedroom, the dining room and living room, and the full bathroom. The country kitchen has lots of work-space and cupboard space, and solid wood floors. The second floor of the home has two more bedrooms and a half-bath. The full basement has both stair access and exterior walkout, with a bulkhead door. There is plenty of room to utilize the space as a one-car garage or use it as a workshop. Outside, there is a deck looking off into the back yard. Have a plan!
